title: NOAA N43 P-3 Radar Imagery - storm relative [NOAA/AOML/HRD]
summary: This dataset contains imagery of the N43RF airborne radar data collected during Dennis, Emily, Gert, Katrina, Ophelia, and Rita. The imagery are in storm relative coordinates. This dataset contains both mpeg movies of entire days, and GIF images of individual sweeps. These data were downloaded from the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration (NOAA) Office of Oceanic and Atmospheric Research Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory (AOML) Hurricane Research Division (HRD) Mission Catalog 2005 Radar Data pages for Dennis, Emily, Gert, Katrina, Ophelia, and Rita.
name: SPECTRAL/ENGINEERING > RADAR > RADAR IMAGERY
